Grid Finder - run instructions

1. Save files into project folder with structure:
  package.json
  server.js
  best_times.json (optional)
  /public/index.html
  /public/app.js
  /public/style.css

2. Install and start:
  npm install
  npm start

3. Open in browser:
  http://localhost:3000

Notes:
- Uses Socket.IO for realtime. Server authoritative countdown and best-time updates.
- Best times persisted to best_times.json when updated.
- Frontend is vanilla JS; SVG grid rendering is in /public/app.js.
